name: PassiveExpiringMap_containsKeyTest
description: Unit tests for the containsKey method of PassiveExpiringMap.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_KeyExistsAndNotExpired
test_cases.description: Tests that the containsKey method returns true when the key exists and is not expired.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_KeyExistsButExpired
test_cases.description: Tests that the containsKey method returns false when the key exists but is expired.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_KeyDoesNotExist
test_cases.description: Tests that the containsKey method returns false when the key does not exist.
